      "cookedHtml": "<p>For someone using calendar a lot - its not easy to find ’ today’ . Can it be highlighted better?<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/9/79286d62db70f8fcf4d7813a0ea0fa15a2fb7e07.png\" title=\"MicrosoftTeams-image (1)\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/9/79286d62db70f8fcf4d7813a0ea0fa15a2fb7e07_2_690x374.png\" alt=\"MicrosoftTeams-image (1)\" width=\"690\" height=\"374\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">MicrosoftTeams-image (1)</span><span class=\"informations\">2284×1238 253 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
