      "id": 137148,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2023-07-31T20:39:53.002Z",
      "author": "BiancaT (Bianca Taylor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/aspilm\">@aspilm</a>,</p>\n<p>You can click the <strong>today</strong> option at the top of the calendar to zoom into the tasks specific to the current day - is this what you’re looking for?</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/c/8c0b1ca6ee4b57a4df11bb023645dcf7dbf0fae4.png\" title=\"79286d62db70f8fcf4d7813a0ea0fa15a2fb7e07\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/c/8c0b1ca6ee4b57a4df11bb023645dcf7dbf0fae4_2_690x374.png\" alt=\"79286d62db70f8fcf4d7813a0ea0fa15a2fb7e07\" width=\"690\" height=\"374\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">79286d62db70f8fcf4d7813a0ea0fa15a2fb7e07</span><span class=\"informations\">2284×1238 312 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
